---
title: Roast Cauliflower, Chorizo & Goat Cheese Salad with Israeli Couscous & Dill-Parsley Mayo
description: Like a soft teddy bear, tonight’s dish is fluffy and calming. Tufts of roasted cauliflower and other warm veggies poke out of a golden Israeli couscous, mixed with chorizo and creamy goat cheese on top, it will be like eating a very tasty cloud.
